body:
This was translated by Awesome Sauce Translations. I can’t claim I did any of the actual work!

48611 would be a tricky project. I don’t think I can help there, but I did happen to have a more complete version, so I’ve uploaded it for you as 394779.

48611 please.
And thanks for your work.

It’s a happy Clannad doujin!

If you would like to see more Clannad doujinshi translated, please show your support here in the comments.
